abstract_str: __carnufex__ !!__carolinesis__!! pursued reptiles and early mammals on its hind legs . fragments of fossil skull , spine and !!__forelimb__!! were found in north carolina . scientists used 3d scanning to reconstruct the prehistoric predator 's skull . its name means carolina butcher due to the animal 's fearsome appearance . palaeontologists say it was probably the top predator in the __triassic__ period . it lived around 231 million years ago , long before the dinosaurs dominated .
